manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: 5Feet/1.5m 3-in-1 Mutltiple Charging Cables (3-Pack) This multi charging cable with 3 different USB ports, including Micro USB, Type C, and iOS connectors. Support to charger most of the cell phones available on market. iOS Connector: Compatible with Phone 13 Pro Max/13 Pro/13 mini/13/12 Pro Max/12 Pro/12 mini/12/11/11 Pro/Xs /Xs Max/Xr/X/ 8/8 Plus Phone 7/7 Plus/6s/ 6 Plus, Pad Air/ Air 2, Pad Pro, Pad mini Pod touch. USB C Connector: Support fast charge.Compatible with Samsung Galaxy S21 S20 S10 S9 S8 S7 S6, Note 10 9 8 7 6, New Book 2015, Book Pro 2016, ChromeBook Pixel 2015, Google Nexus 6P/5X, OnePlus 2/3/4/5, Huawei P9 P10 P20 P30, Lumia 950, Lumia 950 XL , HTC, Xiaomi, Nokia, Moto and more. Micro USB Connector: With fast charging.Compatible with most Android and Windows phones, tablets and many other devices including HTC / Nokia / LG / Sony / GPS device.

Fast Charger & Sync Cable The thicker copper core wire inside can realize faster and more stable charging, which is 30% faster than ordinary multi cables. The thickened aluminum foil signal shielding layer can realize more stable data transmission on the iOS interface. Note: Only the iOS connector support DATA TRANSFER.

5feet and 3-in-1 Design 5ft is the perfect length for a charging cable for various applications, 3-in-1 design, makes the cord portable and only need one cable when you are on a business trip or traveling. Features: Length: 5Ft (150cm) Material: Nylon Braided + Aluminium Alloy Packing: 2 × 3-in-1 USB multi charging cable Warm tips: The maximum total output current of iOS port is 2.4A, Type-C is 3A and Micro-USB is 2A (For total, not for each end) The actual charging speed is determined by the highest output that the wall charger can provide, you can charge multiple devices at the same time with a 5V/3A wall charger, particularly suitable for family or guests.

Hard-Wearing Exterior Made with tough, Double-Braided Nylon for a cable that lasts longer and looks better than other cables. Flexible and Durable The Multi USB fast charging cable using high-quality heat resistant aluminum alloys terminals to increase reliability and durability, with a 15,000+ bend lifespan could withstand a variety of daily connection needs and long-term use. 5ft(150cm) Perfect Length The Charging Cable is Suitable for Use in Different Occasions.Even when you're out or traveling, it's easy to carry and long enough to recharge the back seat.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Versatile, reliable cable
reviews.reviewText: This cable checks all my important boxes: Charges multiple devices, Reliable (no issues in 30 days of use), Economical. One unexpected bonus: the red color makes it easy to spot in a tangle of cables or in a dark backpack. I will buy more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great to have around the house and for traveling
reviews.reviewText: My husband and I have android but the rest of my family has iphones so when they visit it is always a challenge to dig out an iphone charger from somewhere. AND I found multiple times when I was traveling I forgot my kindle charger, so I decided to get some of these prior to theirs visit and a busy summer travel season. Worked great to have all the different chargers in one cord. Also added benefit is that you can charge multiple devices with one cord all at once. over all I highly recommend. we now have one of these as a permanent fixture in our kitchen and living room so that people aren't replacing chargers constantly.

reviews.reviewText: These cables did not work after several uses.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good working charger cable
reviews.reviewText: This cable allowed me to be able to charge a variety of things. Instead of carrying 3 different cables I only need one. So far cables work with no problems

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a must have for anyone who wants to decrease the number of cords you have. I have bought 5 boxes of these so far, and they work as described. This product charges the devices extremely fast, even when two or all of the cords are being used at once. With the braided cord, it adds a durability layer, extending the lifespan of the product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 2nd time buying these.
reviews.reviewText: Great product at what I think is a pretty good price. This is the second set I’ve bought and the way people admire them, I may need more. I have one at my office on my desk powering several different things, and now my wife swiped the one I use at home. Good deal, buy them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Worked Good for 3 months, then Lightning Cord Stopped Working
reviews.reviewText: The lightning cord lasted only three months, but both USBs have lasted over a year. Of course, I use them sparingly, so I'm wondering how reliable they are. I have found a much better quality cable for the same price on Amazon. They are silver, if that helps you at all.Cheers
